# Svelte Restrictions

## Prohibited Patterns
- Do not use JSX syntax
- Do not use slot elements
- Do not use deprecated Svelte features
- Do not use inline styles
- Do not use global styles without proper scoping

## Allowed Alternatives
- Use Svelte template syntax instead of JSX
- Use `{@render ...}` instead of slots
- Use modern Svelte features (runes)
- Use CSS custom properties for dynamic styles
- Use `:global()` for necessary global styles
